@page "/training"

<h1>Training at Tiverton Waterpolo Club</h1>
<br />
<p>
    Tiverton Waterpolo Club follows the same outline development pathway as the other aquatic disciplines:
</p>
<p>
    As the club was formed less than 2yrs ago, we focus on Fundamentals stage for our Minis; 
    transitioning to Learn To Play for our younger Juniors and Train to Train and Train to 
    Compete for our more able Juniors and Seniors." to read: "We focus on Fundamentals and 
    transitioning to Learn To Play for our younger Juniors and Train to Train and Train to 
    Compete for our more able Juniors and Seniors. We also offer an inclusive grassroots 
    senior session aimed at physical wellbeing and enjoying the fundamentals of the game.
</p>
<p>
    The underpinning principle is to have fun!
</p>
