        <td rowspan="3">Training to Compete</td>
        <td>1) Developing individual and team tactics.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>2) Develop individuals to become match fit.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>3) Experience and exposure to more competitive competitions.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td rowspan="3">Training to Win</td>
        <td>1) Individualised training components.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
